1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:41,530
We managed to make it to the sea.

3
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,520
Yeah.

4
00:01:44,450 --> 00:01:48,870
Now to just get to back to the Sunny.

5
00:01:51,260 --> 00:01:55,090
It's so sweet, I'm really happy!

6
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:58,260
What? I don't like it.
It's sticky all over...

7
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:01,830
See? The helm is slippery...

8
00:02:01,830 --> 00:02:06,190
Watch out! Move out of my way, fish-san !

9
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:12,270
Brook! Isn't that a mermaid?!

10
00:02:12,270 --> 00:02:14,790
What?! A mermaid-san ?!

11
00:02:14,790 --> 00:02:16,880
Oh, it's a merman!

12
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,110
Oh...

13
00:02:20,490 --> 00:02:23,580
What is he doing? Fishing, maybe?

14
00:02:24,390 --> 00:02:27,620
I don't care anymore...

15
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:42,120
As long as Big Mom is on a ravenous rampage,
all we can do is run!

16
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,870
"Ravenous rampage"? What's that?

17
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,480
She's having a tantrum!

18
00:02:50,890 --> 00:02:52,970
Until she can eat what she craves...

19
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:58,320
she'll keep rampaging without discretion!

20
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:02,170
Wedding...

21
00:03:02,170 --> 00:03:06,050
cake!

22
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,520
She's almost unconscious...

23
00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:15,780
What she craves this time
seems to be a wedding cake!

24
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:26,000
Maybe because she didn't get
to eat the cake at the wedding!

25
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,920
Luffy! You shouldn't have ruined the cake!

26
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:35,010
But the plan succeeded!

27
00:03:35,010 --> 00:03:38,260
And I've never gotten to eat
such a delicious cake before!

28
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,640
Were you eating during the mission?!

29
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:53,770
I ate it too! It was delicious!

30
00:03:53,770 --> 00:03:58,200
Anyway, hurry up!
I'm sure we're close to the Sunny !

31
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:04,490
It's really hard to tell if we're going
straight through these woods!

32
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:24,180
Is this really the right way?!

33
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:26,100
Oh! Look!

34
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:30,020
That river looks familiar!

35
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:34,820
The Sunny must be right across the river!

36
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:37,150
Wait a minute!

37
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:45,870
If I'm remembering right,
that bridge was broken before!

38
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,170
You're right...

39
00:04:47,170 --> 00:04:50,790
If these woods are our enemy,
we can't trust anything!

40
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:55,290
They're trying to fool us...

41
00:04:57,020 --> 00:05:02,180
so I'm sure they're shifting the landscape
to confuse us...

42
00:05:02,180 --> 00:05:04,010
In other words,

43
00:05:04,010 --> 00:05:07,310
this isn't the place we think it is!

44
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:11,510
Lola's vivre card won't help us anymore...

45
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:14,770
Yeah, since Mama herself is right behind us!

46
00:05:14,770 --> 00:05:18,280
That gives you all the more reason
to keep feeding him, Nami.

47
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:20,480
Yeah... Zeus!

48
00:05:28,110 --> 00:05:29,610
It's...

49
00:05:29,610 --> 00:05:32,040
It's delicious! So delicious!

50
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:37,370
If we let Zeus go back to Mama,
there's no way we'll be able to escape.

51
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:45,740
Come back, Zeus!

52
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:53,040
If we're too slow, she'll catch up!

53
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:56,090
Oh, no! I'm gonna get scolded!

54
00:05:56,090 --> 00:05:57,460
Hey!

55
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:58,680
Prometheus!

56
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:03,350
Why are you disobeying Mama's orders, Zeus?!

57
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:05,840
Zeus! Look at me!

58
00:06:07,010 --> 00:06:13,060
I've got an exquisite Weather Egg
filled with juicy thunderclouds!

59
00:06:13,060 --> 00:06:14,850
Wow! That looks great!

60
00:06:14,850 --> 00:06:17,940
Whoa, wait, Zeus!

61
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:22,690
Hey, sun!

62
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:26,530
How dare you...

63
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:30,450
burn up the tree guy!

64
00:06:31,450 --> 00:06:33,100
Gum-Gum...

65
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:36,380
Hawk Gatling!

66
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,970
That's our Luffy!

67
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,860
What the...?!

68
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,780
Don't think...

69
00:06:57,260 --> 00:07:00,780
that you can beat me with just that!

70
00:07:00,790 --> 00:07:02,660
Oh! Ow, ow, ow!

71
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:06,710
If armament haki doesn't work,
he'll be harder to deal with than a logia!

72
00:07:06,710 --> 00:07:09,250
I'm gonna burn you all to death!

73
00:07:09,250 --> 00:07:12,380
Ow, ow! It's hot! Ouch, ouch, ouch!

74
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,740
Come back, Zeus!

75
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:23,170
I will! I will, but...

76
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:27,160
I wanna eat just one more juicy thundercloud!

77
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,270
You...

78
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,470
Jinbe!

79
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:35,670
Cross the bridge now, everyone!

80
00:07:35,670 --> 00:07:36,490
Okay!

81
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:38,910
Spear Wave!

82
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,360
Rain Shower!

83
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:44,050
Did it work?!

84
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:45,330
Of course!

85
00:07:45,330 --> 00:07:48,360
He's just a mass of compressed fire,

86
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,960
which makes him nothing
but a big, talking flame.

87
00:07:53,090 --> 00:07:55,090
You bastard...

88
00:07:59,770 --> 00:08:01,180
Are they...?!

89
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,480
Get ready, Straw Hat crew!

90
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,230
The Seducing Woods will be...

91
00:08:08,230 --> 00:08:10,480
...where you die!

92
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,190
Drop dead!

93
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:14,400
What?! I can't believe they caught up to us!

94
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:17,450
The homies must've shifted the landscape!

95
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:31,280
They're closing in from both sides...

96
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:34,180
Then we only have one option...

97
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:37,470
Yeah, let's kick their asses!

98
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:55,580
Your name's Pedro, right?
I saw you five years ago, too...

99
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,340
Uh-oh!

100
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,730
You silly rabbit!

101
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:25,460
Garchu!

102
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:28,780
Stop!

103
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,620
Yes!

104
00:09:34,620 --> 00:09:36,330
Brother Tablet!

105
00:09:36,330 --> 00:09:38,560
You'd better pay attention!

106
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,340
Diable Jambe!

107
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:55,270
Flambage Shot!

108
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:07,860
Gum-Gum...

109
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,790
Eagle Bazooka!

110
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,890
Don't get separated,

111
00:10:25,890 --> 00:10:28,140
or we'll never see each other again!

112
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:28,890
Okay!

113
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,000
Yeah!

114
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,670
Okay!

115
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:33,730
Luffy, stop Carrot!

116
00:10:33,730 --> 00:10:34,610
Yeah!

117
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:48,160
I won't let you get away!

118
00:10:49,330 --> 00:10:50,580
Duck!

119
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:07,070
Take this!

120
00:11:07,070 --> 00:11:08,490
Watch out!

121
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:12,470
You...!

122
00:11:24,050 --> 00:11:26,890
Cake!

123
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:30,880
Is this it?

124
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,640
I'll eat that!

125
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,720
Zeus!

126
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:36,270
It's a delicious cloud!

127
00:11:39,110 --> 00:11:40,120
What?

128
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,660
Is that...

129
00:11:41,660 --> 00:11:43,540
What is it?!

130
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:48,710
So delicious!

131
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:58,180
My Weather Egg is inside of Zeus...!

132
00:11:58,180 --> 00:12:02,010
What is he doing?!

133
00:12:02,010 --> 00:12:03,930
Hey, Zeus!

134
00:12:10,130 --> 00:12:12,410
Hey, guys!

135
00:12:12,410 --> 00:12:15,980
Sorry we kept you waiting!

136
00:12:30,010 --> 00:12:31,720
Why are they...

137
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,720
on the Sunny ?

138
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:40,430
I'm sorry. Your friends aren't here. Lick!

139
00:12:49,070 --> 00:12:51,150
Zeus Breeze...

140
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:56,190
Tempo!

141
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:28,910
Don't tell me Luffy and the others are...

142
00:13:32,330 --> 00:13:34,080
Is that...

143
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:40,290
It looks like Mama finished them off with Zeus.
Mama'll be here soon.

144
00:13:40,290 --> 00:13:41,680
Lick!

145
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:45,530
He's saying that,
but they'll be fine, right?

146
00:13:45,530 --> 00:13:47,900
Yeah, I'm sure they will!

147
00:13:49,730 --> 00:13:53,620
Lick! I guess your friends are dead,

148
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:57,040
so what are you two gonna do?

149
00:13:57,040 --> 00:14:00,280
Even if you risk your lives
and try to take back this ship,

150
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:02,760
none of your friends will return.

151
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:12,520
If you want to escape from here in that submarine,
I don't mind letting just the two of you leave.

152
00:14:19,740 --> 00:14:21,460
No, thanks.

153
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:27,370
Kung Fu Point!

154
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:32,300
Get off the ship, you bastards!
The Sunny is ours!

155
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,100
Do you want to fight?

156
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,840
Of course!

157
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:43,760
We'll save the Sunny !

158
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:47,600
I guess you want to die. Lick!

159
00:14:59,590 --> 00:15:03,240
Everyone, on your feet!
Let's get this show started!

160
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,660
Yeah!

161
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:10,640
The forest is... What happened?!

162
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,290
Is everyone okay?!

163
00:15:12,290 --> 00:15:14,090
Rabiyan, go faster!

164
00:15:14,090 --> 00:15:15,640
Okay!

165
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:22,680
I'm sorry I asked you to help, Sister...

166
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:27,430
It's okay! It's been a long time
since we baked a cake together!

167
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:30,750
On top of that...

168
00:15:35,110 --> 00:15:37,460
You're going?! Are you kidding?!

169
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:43,660
Bege! Didn't I tell you?!
The Straw Hats saved my younger sister Lola's life!

170
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:47,000
But, Chiffon, it's dangerous! I'm worried!

171
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:50,480
He's right-rero !
You must escape with us-rero !

172
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:52,540
Oh, I'm sorry. That was too loud...

173
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:55,420
We can't leave without you, ma'am!

174
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:56,920
Come back, Chiffon!

175
00:15:56,920 --> 00:16:00,590
Dangerous?! Yes, I know that!

176
00:16:03,430 --> 00:16:08,670
"Thank you for saving Lola."
It's too easy to just say that.

177
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:13,690
Sincerity will be proven when you
help the ones you're indebted to!

178
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:16,570
You're right, but...

179
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:22,280
That's how you do your duty,
right, darling?

180
00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:26,330
If something happens to me...

181
00:16:29,330 --> 00:16:31,560
please take care of...

182
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:32,790
Pez for me!

183
00:16:39,210 --> 00:16:41,170
Chiffon!

184
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:44,430
Ma'am!

185
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:55,150
I have to save Nami and the others
and return to my family!

186
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:57,380
Sister! There he is!

187
00:16:58,570 --> 00:17:01,490
Pudding? Were you listening?

188
00:17:01,490 --> 00:17:03,950
S... Sanji-san is...

189
00:17:06,120 --> 00:17:07,730
S... S...

190
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,700
Sanji...

191
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:16,110
S...

192
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:17,420
S...

193
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,340
S...

194
00:17:19,970 --> 00:17:22,090
Sanji's there! That fool!

195
00:17:22,090 --> 00:17:23,690
Say what?!

196
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,710
That was pretty powerful!

197
00:17:30,710 --> 00:17:34,340
My Clima-Tact isn't able
to generate lightning like that!

198
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:36,200
With that much power...

199
00:17:39,780 --> 00:17:41,400
Where's Big Mom?

200
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,800
She must've been hit directly!

201
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,710
She's probably in that giant hole!

202
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:49,220
Did we just take down Big Mom?!

203
00:17:58,870 --> 00:17:59,690
What is it?

204
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:10,590
Wedding...

205
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:12,130
Big Mom's voice?!

206
00:18:12,130 --> 00:18:14,180
I thought so...

207
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:16,570
...cake!

208
00:18:16,570 --> 00:18:18,500
Is she alive?!

209
00:18:21,320 --> 00:18:25,350
She's not someone we can beat that easily...

210
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:28,860
She's climbing up!

211
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:37,160
Is the hole too deep for her to climb out?

212
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:39,250
Let's run while she's in there!

213
00:18:39,250 --> 00:18:42,620
Yeah. While Big Mom can't move!

214
00:18:45,430 --> 00:18:48,500
No, she's already on her way...

215
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:51,600
The ground is...

216
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:52,800
No way!

217
00:19:02,620 --> 00:19:07,310
There's no stopping Big Mom
during a ravenous rampage!

218
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:10,600
Wedding...

219
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:13,570
cake!

220
00:19:14,190 --> 00:19:16,070
Oh no! Run!

221
00:19:16,710 --> 00:19:21,080
Wedding...

222
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:23,700
No... The ground's gonna crack open!

223
00:19:25,890 --> 00:19:27,080
Here she comes!

224
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:34,010
Run!

225
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:38,180
...cake!

226
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:42,180
Bring it to me!

227
00:19:45,240 --> 00:19:48,330
I know you guys have it!

228
00:19:49,950 --> 00:19:53,580
Straw Hat!

229
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,340
She's at the top!

230
00:19:59,420 --> 00:20:00,980
Straw Hat crew!

231
00:20:00,980 --> 00:20:01,600
What?

232
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,010
Pudding! Chiffon!

233
00:20:03,010 --> 00:20:06,970
Oh, Pudding! What's wrong with you?!
You fooled us!

234
00:20:06,970 --> 00:20:09,310
To stop Mama's ravenous rampage–

235
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:12,980
See? We should've tied her up earlier!

236
00:20:12,980 --> 00:20:14,600
To stop Mama's–

237
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:18,860
But why's Chiffon with her?!
I thought she ran away with Bege's group!

238
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:19,700
To stop Mama's–

239
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:20,440
Wanna fight?!

240
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:23,150
No, I don't! Listen to me!

241
00:20:23,150 --> 00:20:25,620
Pudding-chan, you're okay!

242
00:20:26,490 --> 00:20:30,330
I'm glad that your pretty face isn't hurt!

243
00:20:30,330 --> 00:20:33,670
So lovely! So lovely!

244
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,670
Pudding, get it together!

245
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,590
Oh, no! Mama's coming!

246
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:41,800
Mama!

247
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:45,100
We have no time!
Pudding, get right to the point!

248
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,140
Okay!

249
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:50,860
Pathetic! You fools!
You're not gonna make it!

250
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:53,800
Even if you escape by ship,

251
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:59,430
Mama will chase you to the farthest sea
and sink you to the ocean floor!

252
00:21:00,870 --> 00:21:02,700
What did you say?!

253
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:07,430
That's not right, Pudding!
What are you talking about?!

254
00:21:07,430 --> 00:21:10,960
You're right! You're right!
What am I saying?!

255
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,200
Listen!

256
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:18,570
Mama believes that you guys stole the wedding cake
she really wanted to eat!

257
00:21:18,570 --> 00:21:22,060
What?! We don't have a cake!

258
00:21:22,060 --> 00:21:29,060
I know! But right now, Mama's in a state where she'll
chase you across the ocean to get that cake!

259
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:32,600
That's right! So, Sanji! Come here!

260
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:38,660
Watch as your friends get killed by Mama
and go through hell!

261
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:45,160
That's not right!

262
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:49,210
– What are you talking about?!
– You're right! I wanna disappear!

263
00:21:49,210 --> 00:21:52,590
If that's what you came to say,
go away, you jerks!

264
00:21:52,590 --> 00:21:54,840
Wait a minute! That wasn't it!

265
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:56,440
Black Leg Sanji!

266
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,360
What?

267
00:21:57,360 --> 00:22:01,090
Pudding told me
you're good at making sweets, too!

268
00:22:01,090 --> 00:22:04,510
Yeah, I'm an excellent chef.

269
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:08,380
Okay! Then, help us bake the cake!

270
00:22:08,380 --> 00:22:11,800
We'll make a cake that's capable of stopping Mama,

271
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:14,230
and then we'll help you guys escape!

272
00:22:14,230 --> 00:22:16,150
Chiffon! Why?!

273
00:22:16,150 --> 00:22:21,570
I wanna repay you for saving Lola!
And I'll risk my life to do it!

274
00:22:21,570 --> 00:22:23,620
Thank you, Chiffon!

275
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:24,450
Uh-huh!

276
00:22:24,450 --> 00:22:30,540
Hmph! Maybe that's the end result!
But unlike my sister, I'm not doing it for you!

277
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:35,480
The cake that I was planning to bake for myself
happened to be the one Mama is craving now!

278
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:40,090
A-A-And I just happened to be in this area!
I didn't know you guys were here!

279
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:49,520
S-So it's not like I came all the way to stop her
because I didn't want you to die, Sanji...

280
00:22:50,180 --> 00:22:51,640
-san !

281
00:22:55,750 --> 00:22:58,440
Her emotions are like a roller coaster!

282
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,800
I see! That's good!

283
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,700
Where can we bake the cake?!

284
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:05,880
We have extra ingredients
at Chocolat Town!

285
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:12,320
First we'll go to Chocolat Town
and bake the cake as fast as we can!

286
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:16,520
Then we'll carry it on a ship
and deliver it to you!

287
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:20,400
And we'll let Mama, who will be chasing you, eat the cake!

288
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:26,610
That way, we can distract her attention away
from you! So just hang in there until then!

289
00:23:27,320 --> 00:23:28,410
Is she coming?!

290
00:23:28,890 --> 00:23:31,620
Wedding...

291
00:23:31,620 --> 00:23:35,100
Once you sail out to sea,
you'll have enemies in front of you, too!

292
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:38,290
But I believe you guys can handle it!

293
00:23:38,290 --> 00:23:39,250
We will!

294
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:41,060
Then... I'll come with you!

295
00:23:41,060 --> 00:23:41,600
What?!

296
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:43,300
Yeah, hurry up and hop on!

297
00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:47,980
W-W-Wait!
Who said you could ride with us, idiot?!

298
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:50,910
...cake!

299
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,760
She got up!

300
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:07,560
The cake you guys are baking
is the only way to stop Big Mom!

301
00:24:07,560 --> 00:24:09,150
Uh-huh!

302
00:24:09,150 --> 00:24:10,630
Guys!

303
00:24:10,630 --> 00:24:14,240
I'm gonna leave you for now,
but I promise I'll return!

304
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,280
Uh-huh!

305
00:24:15,990 --> 00:24:17,690
Okay!

306
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:23,490
Yeah, I know you will!

307
00:24:31,060 --> 00:24:32,450
Hey!

308
00:24:32,450 --> 00:24:33,660
Pudding!

309
00:24:33,660 --> 00:24:35,050
Chiffon!

310
00:24:38,430 --> 00:24:40,850
Oh no! She's gonna do it again!

311
00:24:43,810 --> 00:24:44,930
Get away!

312
00:24:47,020 --> 00:24:51,610
What are you doing here?!

313
00:24:51,610 --> 00:24:54,110
Luffy! I'll see you at sea!

314
00:24:54,110 --> 00:24:56,070
I'm counting on you, Sanji!

315
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:01,410
Hegemony!

316
00:25:44,340 --> 00:25:47,500
Enough already...

317
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:49,380
That was close.

318
00:25:49,380 --> 00:25:51,100
Is everyone okay?

319
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:54,440
Let's go! The Sunny is waiting for us
at the coast!

320
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:59,080
Wait! They're going the wrong way.

321
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:05,480
Rabiyan, go down again!
Fly straight from the previous spot to the coastline!

322
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,830
Roger!

323
00:26:07,870 --> 00:26:10,040
Luffy-kun and everyone!

324
00:26:10,040 --> 00:26:13,710
Wait! You're going the wrong way!
There's a wall ahead of you!

325
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:16,670
What? Pudding? It's the nice Pudding!

326
00:26:16,670 --> 00:26:19,370
I thought we were going straight.

327
00:26:19,370 --> 00:26:21,550
Of course, we've been fooled.

328
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:23,790
Everyone! The coastline is this way!

329
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,600
Okay, let's go!

330
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:28,230
We won't let you leave!

331
00:26:30,560 --> 00:26:32,400
Leave them to me!

332
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:35,230
Memories Fil:

333
00:26:43,450 --> 00:26:45,280
Flashback!

334
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:51,750
Oh, I need to go shopping.

335
00:26:53,120 --> 00:26:55,780
Big Brother hit me!

336
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:57,840
I need to walk the dog.

337
00:26:57,840 --> 00:27:01,640
My son is missing.
Has anyone seen him?

338
00:27:02,210 --> 00:27:03,930
What's going on?

339
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:06,850
In any case, let's run before it's too late!

340
00:27:07,250 --> 00:27:08,640
What's going on?

341
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:10,390
They're memories from the previous owners

342
00:27:10,390 --> 00:27:13,260
of the souls that were
used to create the Homies.

343
00:27:13,260 --> 00:27:16,360
Those memories are returning
to them temporarily.

344
00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:19,900
While they're confused,
Mama has no control over them.

345
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:23,280
So Luffy-kun and the others
can escape from the woods now.

346
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:25,990
I see. Thank you, Pudding-chan!

347
00:27:29,410 --> 00:27:33,330
Why?! How long have you been there, Sanji...

348
00:27:33,330 --> 00:27:34,340
-san ?!

349
00:27:34,340 --> 00:27:36,020
Well, just for a little bit.

350
00:27:36,020 --> 00:27:37,400
What?!

351
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,430
How did you not notice?!

352
00:27:39,430 --> 00:27:42,800
Now, Pudding-chan,
let's rush to Chocolat Town.

353
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:45,220
J-Jump off and swim, you idiot!

354
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:48,350
Your eye is beautiful even when you're mad...

355
00:27:52,260 --> 00:27:54,060
Are you okay, Pudding?

356
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:58,650
I-I'm fine... D-D-Don't mess with me!

357
00:27:58,650 --> 00:28:02,230
O-Or I'll kill you, Sanji...

358
00:28:02,230 --> 00:28:03,610
-san !

359
00:28:05,130 --> 00:28:07,940
I see the coastline ahead!

360
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,100
Hurry up!

361
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:13,900
We made it!
But... is Pudding really on our side now?!

362
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:19,030
I don't know! We shouldn't lower our guard
until we escape their territory!

363
00:28:23,270 --> 00:28:25,910
I won't let you get away!

364
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,500
Hey, Zeus!

365
00:28:28,500 --> 00:28:30,880
How could you do that?!

366
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:39,630
Why did you hit us, too?!

367
00:28:39,630 --> 00:28:43,280
I'm sorry... I didn't mean for that to happen...

368
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:48,400
I don't care what you meant to do!
You better pay attention next time!

369
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:51,150
Yes, you're right...

370
00:28:51,150 --> 00:28:56,110
But they were so delicious...
Those thundercloud eggs.

371
00:28:56,110 --> 00:28:56,940
Huh?!

372
00:28:56,940 --> 00:29:02,490
Hey, are you really listening to me?!
Mama's orders are absolute!

373
00:29:02,490 --> 00:29:04,580
I know...

374
00:29:07,220 --> 00:29:09,490
Give it to me!

375
00:29:09,490 --> 00:29:14,840
My wedding cake!

376
00:29:14,840 --> 00:29:15,710
Oh, no!

377
00:29:18,590 --> 00:29:19,670
Dodge it!

378
00:29:26,660 --> 00:29:27,890
Damn...

379
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:30,470
That was close!

380
00:29:30,470 --> 00:29:32,140
Thank you, Jinbe!

381
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:55,280
You're quite the match for our Chess Peacekeepers, skeleton...

382
00:29:56,830 --> 00:29:58,810
It's because I am...

383
00:29:58,810 --> 00:30:01,370
Soul King!

384
00:30:01,370 --> 00:30:05,380
Enemies keep coming out of the mirror...

385
00:30:08,090 --> 00:30:12,970
They're coming from the mirror in Nami and Robin's room. Will they be mad if we break it?

386
00:30:12,970 --> 00:30:16,810
If we can break it, let's break it.
We'll apologize later.

387
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:21,350
Who are you gonna apologize to? Lick.

388
00:30:21,350 --> 00:30:23,800
You saw the lightning earlier, didn't you?

389
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:27,030
None of them are returning to this ship.

390
00:30:30,490 --> 00:30:34,790
I've been saying that I want
to show mercy on you two.

391
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:40,460
No matter how hard you try,
our soldiers will come through the mirror endlessly.

392
00:30:40,460 --> 00:30:44,760
And you guys will use up
all of your energy eventually.

393
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:51,140
If you submit right here, right now,
I'll at least spare your life...

394
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:53,480
Just give up already.

395
00:30:55,010 --> 00:30:57,690
What a foolish conversation.

396
00:30:58,650 --> 00:31:03,010
We're sick and tired of responding to that.

397
00:31:04,730 --> 00:31:07,320
We just want you to get off of our ship.

398
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:10,200
The Sunny is our ship!

399
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:14,910
Do you really wanna fight me?

400
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:30,100
I see...

401
00:31:30,100 --> 00:31:35,220
It seems you don't really value your own life...

402
00:31:35,220 --> 00:31:36,890
All right.

403
00:31:36,890 --> 00:31:40,110
I'll kill you with my own hands.

404
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:42,270
Lick.

405
00:31:50,370 --> 00:31:52,890
Oh! That's the edge of the forest!

406
00:31:52,890 --> 00:31:56,220
All right! Let's go straight to Cacao Island!

407
00:32:02,360 --> 00:32:04,490
Brook! Chopper!

408
00:32:04,490 --> 00:32:06,660
Is that your ship?

409
00:32:06,660 --> 00:32:09,240
Yeah, it's getting attacked.

410
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:11,800
I guess they were ambushed...

411
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:15,560
Oh, no! Our older brothers are there!

412
00:32:16,950 --> 00:32:20,750
Our older brothers are attacking
Sanji-san's friends...

413
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:22,880
Hmph! Your friends are screwed!

414
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:27,010
That'll teach ya!
Those two are no match for our brothers!

415
00:32:27,010 --> 00:32:31,030
Your friends will be swallowed by the sea!

416
00:32:32,130 --> 00:32:34,460
What are you saying, Pudding?!

417
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:38,930
Oh, no! That's not what I meant to say!

418
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:43,050
What do you wanna do?
Should we go down to the ship?

419
00:32:44,230 --> 00:32:47,730
No, I'll come along with Pudding-chan.

420
00:32:47,730 --> 00:32:48,770
What?

421
00:32:50,110 --> 00:32:53,620
Are you sure?
We'll keep on going then!

422
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:56,740
Yeah, we don't need to worry about them.

423
00:32:57,410 --> 00:33:01,250
Instead, let's get started...

424
00:33:02,870 --> 00:33:07,710
on the cake that will make Big Mom faint!

